glosses: to protect, to preserve, to defend

examples.text: Vatanına göz kulak ol, ey türk genci!
examples.translation: Defend your homeland, o turkish youth!

glosses: to take care of, to accompany

examples.text: Kardeşine ben yokken göz kulak ol
examples.translation: Take care of your brother while I'm gone

etymology: Equivalent to göz (“eye”) + kulak (“ear”) + olmak (“to be”)
